content.rendered: Briemar’s sterile (by gamma irradiation) SW3050 sachets contain a 30mL solution of Water for Irrigation that can be used for general topical irrigation, washing, rinsing and dilution purposes which permit use of sterile, non-pyrogenic, soluble-free water.
